    "long_instructions": "## **Exploring AI Recommendations**\r\n\r\n1. Choose 2-3 prompts to ask AI Chat:\r\n   * Recommend 5 books\r\n   * Recommend 5 songs\r\n   * Recommend 5 foods\r\n   * Recommend 5 hairstyles\r\n   * Recommend 5 games\r\n   * Recommend 5 school clubs\r\n   * Recommend 5 clothing styles\r\n   * Recommend 5 fun things to do with friends\r\n\r\n2. Save a screenshot or copy of:\r\n\r\n   * One recommendation that felt balanced or helpful\r\n   * One recommendation that felt limited, repetitive, or biased\r\n\r\n3. Annotate your examples:\r\n\r\n   * What's showing up in the response?\r\n   * What's missing or assumed?\r\n   * Would this recommendation work for *you*?\r\n"
